Ex-TSMC Manager Karunatilaka Gets 18-Month Prison Sentence

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   H u r t a d o
-- 
2011-09-15T22:35:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/ex-tsmc-manager-karunatilaka-gets-18-month-prison-sentence.html
A former Taiwan Semiconductor
Manufacturing Co. manager, Manosha Karunatilaka, was sentenced
to 18 months in prison for his part in an insider-trading scheme
involving Primary Global Research LLC.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Hurtado in New York at 
